# KinoJspreadsheetCe

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:kino_jspreadsheet_ce, "~> 0.1.0"},
  {:kino_vega_lite, "~> 0.1.13"},
  {:explorer, "~> 0.11.1"}
])
```

## Programmatic creation and data population

```elixir
